<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>435</hymn_number>
<title>I HOPE TO MEETYOU ALL IN GLORY</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Lopi taka hun tuok ka kinem,
 Damsung huihpi a beih tieng;
 Thusim deihum chuh gen ka kinem,
 Luipang vak mun nuom achun.

[V2]
 Luipang vak achun, Luipang hawih achun,
 I pau In ah, kipahna gam achun;
 Hun tuok ding ka kinem (2)
 Lopi takin zawhna lukhuk khun.

[V3]
 2. Lopi taka hun tuok ka kinem,
 Hinna thing limnuoi achun;
 Lungsietna zala ei tat ziekin,
 Tanpa pak ding ka kinem.

[V4]
 3. Lopi taka hun tuok ka kinem,
 Hukdampa chutphah velah;
 Hehpih tatna lasa tatsate,
 Chuh zawp ding ka kinem hi.

[V5]
 4. Lopi taka hun tuok ka kinem,
 Ka lei nasep a beih tieng;
 Kipak takin khutin kitui tiu,
 Kumsawt mun vak nuom achun.</lyrics>
</song>